 Galvatron absorbed proto1000.  He wasnt sure is his process with the other 
had been sucessful but it didnt matter. If not he had what he need from him. 
The cacoon broke and he was still in beast mode. He had the ability to 
transform to his other modes now with the power of proto. he couldnt take 
shapes of others only transform into his other modes (robot and drill and 
beast.)by using the liquid transformation process. The absorbtion had healed 
his tail but his wound in his ribs was still quite painfull and depp. His 
armor was lost it was given up to power the transformation and was gone 
forever. If the bot survuved he had an advantage unless he had fled. He began 
internal repairs and saw if the bot had some how gotten out of his trap.
